In the Matter of Z.D.H. (appealed by New Hanover Department of Social Services). No. 358P07. Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 6, 2007. Julia Talbutt, Dean W. Hollandsworth, Wilmington, for New Hanover DSS. David Gordon, Assistant Attorney General, for DHHS. Paula Greene, Elizabethtown, for Guardian. Elva Jess, Southport, for Brunswick Co DSS. Prior report: ___ N.C.App. ___, 646 S.E.2d 374 .

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 24th day of July 2007 by Petitioner (New Hanover DSS) in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 6th day of December 2007."
